{"ja481:0.1":"Jataka ","ja481:0.2":"Terasakanipata ","ja481:0.3":"Ambavagga ","ja481:0.4":"8. Takkariyajataka ","ja481:1.1":"“Ahameva dubbhasitam bhasi balo, ","ja481:1.2":"Bhekovaranne ahimavhayamano; ","ja481:1.3":"Takkariye sobbhamimam patami, ","ja481:1.4":"Na kireva sadhu ativelabhani”. ","ja481:2.1":"“Pappoti macco ativelabhani, ","ja481:2.2":"Bandham vadham sokapariddavanca; ","ja481:2.3":"Attanameva garahasi ettha, ","ja481:2.4":"Acera yam tam nikhananti sobbhe”. ","ja481:3.1":"“Kimevaham tundilamanupucchim, ","ja481:3.2":"Kareyya sam bhataram kalikayam; ","ja481:3.3":"Naggovaham vatthayuganca jino, ","ja481:3.4":"Ayampi attho bahutadisova”. ","ja481:4.1":"“Yo yujjhamananamayujjhamano, ","ja481:4.2":"Mendantaram accupati kulingo; ","ja481:4.3":"So pimsito mendasirehi tattha, ","ja481:4.4":"Ayampi attho bahutadisova. ","ja481:5.1":"Caturo jana potthakamaggahesum, ","ja481:5.2":"Ekanca posam anurakkhamana; ","ja481:5.3":"Sabbeva te bhinnasira sayimsu, ","ja481:5.4":"Ayampi attho bahutadisova. ","ja481:6.1":"Aja yatha velugumbasmim baddha, ","ja481:6.2":"Avakkhipanti asimajjhagacchi; ","ja481:6.3":"Teneva tassa galakavakantam, ","ja481:6.4":"Ayampi attho bahutadisova”. ","ja481:7.1":"“Ime na deva na gandhabbaputta, ","ja481:7.2":"Miga ime atthavasam gata me; ","ja481:7.3":"Ekanca nam sayamase pacantu, ","ja481:7.4":"Ekam punappatarase pacantu”. ","ja481:8.1":"“Satam sahassani dubhasitani, ","ja481:8.2":"Kalampi nagghanti subhasitassa; ","ja481:8.3":"Dubbhasitam sankamano kileso, ","ja481:8.4":"Tasma tunhi kimpurisa na balya”. ","ja481:9.1":"“Ya mesa byahasi pamuncathetam, ","ja481:9.2":"Girinca nam himavantam nayantu; ","ja481:9.3":"Imanca kho dentu mahanasaya, ","ja481:9.4":"Patova nam patarase pacantu”. ","ja481:10.1":"“Pajjunnanatha pasavo, ","ja481:10.2":"pasunatha ayam paja; ","ja481:10.3":"Tvam nathosi maharaja, ","ja481:10.4":"nathoham bhariyaya me; ","ja481:10.5":"Dvinnamannataram natva, ","ja481:10.6":"mutto gaccheyya pabbatam. ","ja481:11.1":"Na ve ninda suparivajjayetha, ","ja481:11.2":"Nana jana sevitabba janinda; ","ja481:11.3":"Yeneva eko labhate pasamsam, ","ja481:11.4":"Teneva anno labhate ninditaram. ","ja481:12.1":"Sabbo loko paricitto aticitto, ","ja481:12.2":"Sabbo loko cittava samhi citte; ","ja481:12.3":"Paccekacitta puthu sabbasatta, ","ja481:12.4":"Kassidha cittassa vasena vatte”. ","ja481:13.1":"“Tunhi ahu kimpuriso sabhariyo, ","ja481:13.2":"Yo dani byahasi bhayassa bhito; ","ja481:13.3":"So dani mutto sukhito arogo, ","ja481:13.4":"Vacakirevatthavati naranan”ti. ","ja481:14.1":"Takkariyajatakam atthamam. "}